social_posts.post_text: I am proud to announce Tate Productions! We specialize in making creative content for social media. Our services include creative direction, social media management, videography, photography, tik tok growth and so much more 🎉🎉 For full information check out my website. Link is in my bio ❤️🙏 Thank you to all the real ones that supported me throughout this journey.

Thank you for supporting my journey as a content creator and creative director. As I continue to grow and expand, I want to take a moment to share a bit about myself with you all. Building a career as a creator has been a labor of love, and it's allowed me to truly express myself creatively. So, let's connect and get to know each other better! Share something about yourself in the comments below and let's build a community of creatives an entrepreneurs. 📸🎥✨

I’ve taken a massive break from social media to really focus on my creative agency. I am excited to finally come back and share all my tips, tricks, failures as well as success stories that comes with being a creator and entrepreneur. All of my videos will be released on Tik Tok starting next week! As a creative director and content creator, we feel the need to always create and post. I want share that if you need to take a break because you are burnt out… it’s okay! We have all been there ❤️

We believe that every brand sponsorship or ad we create has an opportunity to be something truly unique and cool. We approach each project with a fresh perspective and focus on creative direction, videography, and editing to bring the brand to life in a way that resonates with their audience. And when it comes to shooting on location, we don’t just rely on models or actors – I step in as a brand ambassador/influencer to ensure that the brand’s message is delivered with authenticity and personality. 🎬📸 Wearing and promoting  @sheinofficial bathing suit

I grew up watching and learning from @samkolder & @petermckinnon I learned all my skills from endless hours of YouTube. It’s been a long and challenging journey but I am thrilled to have taught myself all the skills I needed to make it happen. Visiting Utah was such a unique experience because I finally felt like a true creative since they all came here to create magic 🙏🙏❤️
Exploring Utah felt like I was stepping onto another planet. The surreal red rock formations and vast desert landscape made me feel like I was on Mars! 🚀

Growing up in the fast-paced, vibrant city of New York taught me to mature quickly and pursue my dreams relentlessly. I was inspired by this incredible city to start my own creative agency, and it hasn't been an easy journey. But through it all, I've learned that being an entrepreneur takes perseverance and determination. I hope my story can inspire other creatives to take the leap and go independent. Here's to chasing our dreams and making them a reality!
Proud to be a born and raised New Yorker ❤️ I wanted to make a short video to showcase the vibes of the city that never sleeps ✨

Nothing hits better than taking a break in nature. It’s the perfect balance of resetting your brain and relaxing in fresh air. As a creative, we need healthy breaks to come up with new concepts. My perfect break was staying at @yosemiteviewlodge

Yosemite’s breathtaking views and riverside retreats make for an unforgettable escape. So grateful for the opportunity to explore this natural wonder and indulge in some much needed rest! Thank you for the lovely stay @yosemiteviewlodge All drone footage was taken OUTSIDE the park 🙏
Nothing beats breakfast on a boat looking over a beautiful river filled with all types of wildlife! Thank you @andazmayakoba.mx for this amazing experience ❤️‍🔥

I’m starting to learn that it is okay to take a pause and have a moment for yourself. I’m excited I’m starting to grow out my creative team and that I do not have to go film every project myself. So here’s to finding balance, appreciating the journey, and savoring the little moments of bliss ✨

I think I’ve become addicted to working on the go. NYC has fueled my hustle to work hard but I need a balance to enjoy life that is why I picked @andazmayakoba.mx to give me the perfect mix of productivity and relaxation ✨
Exploring the castle walls of Europe’s most well-preserved medieval town 🏰

There is something magical about creating content that transports me to a different era, even if it’s just for a moment ✨ I think there is a special charm in exploring places that hold centuries of stories 🏰

#obidos #portugaltravel #cinematographers #vintagefilm
